{"tid":113222,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人玩game玩到刷刷刷戈刻已經開始唔想玩","createTime":"2017-02-08T18:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T12:18:25.000Z","uid":23584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ade18412ff209e82dcc27b925bf4f29370e09ad","tid":113222,"uid":23584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T18:23:11.000Z","msg":"一直都有玩唔同手機game 特別係耐玩既game eg：p&amp;d, 地下城物語，<br />\n但冇一隻玩得過1年 <br />\n初初玩只係為左燒下時間 但玩玩下覺得ok會花多啲時間玩 仲要仲要係咁睇攻略玩 中期發現可以繼續玩會開始買月卡（不過次次未用曬都刪左）<br />\n<br />\n之後仲會迫自己要日日洗曬體力 係咁推主線之類<br />\n但當推到最新既關/要係咁刷野既位  就開始係咁刷野 又要chur住自己刷 到戈時就算拎到自己最想要戈隻野反而唔係興奮 只係覺得好似完成左個任務 然後會諗自己咁曬時間玩隻game係為乜？ 時間係燒到呀   但燒埋我做其他野既時間 之後會係咁屌尻自己做乜咁on9玩呢隻game 最後刪埋   刪完反而輕鬆左。<br />\n但過一排無聊又會搵過第隻   我已經特登唔搵FGO呢啲大坑玩架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋我呢仲play hard既強迫症係咪好撚白痴 就好似我玩Dark soul 要每隻怪都殺過 行曬汁曬全地圖先當爆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申岩岩又刪左曬game"},{"pid":"b76a5e1d1a53f514be0d554cfe0e7ba717dc2794","tid":113222,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:17:03.000Z","msg":"執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你既意思係隻game太重複?"},{"pid":"1811914383a2001b4574b224145250340eb8d268","tid":113222,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:57:32.000Z","msg":"戈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bed816a39715fa1718fa3c4f7adaf28ca02b08","tid":113222,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:21:27.000Z","msg":"因為依家手遊系統千篇一律<br />\n將D角色或資源碎片化斬到極細份要你收集<br />\n升人、升技、或覺醒要打大量資源<br />\n到最後發現只係不停浪費時間升野<br />\n享受戰鬥時間唔多<br />\n<br />\n近年玩過較好玩既<br />\n係皇室戰爭、星球大戰：原力戰場同埋新出老任隻火紋：英雄<br />\n呢三隻都係比較上著重戰鬥既策略同操作多<br />\n就算唔刻意刷野、零課<br />\n剩係玩個戰鬥都好玩<br />\n但呢類較優秀既手遊真係一年無幾多隻<br />\n皇室戰爭係上年美國App Store最賺錢既app<br />\n佢就算課金都可以用黎買到指定既卡<br />\n唔駛抽野靠運<br />\n所以課金堆玩家都唔會插隻game太勁太搵笨"},{"pid":"d1555c91ca703c7e9000bab299bd6cc0efaaba20","tid":113222,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"2016年到依家我玩過好多online手遊<br />\n係得呢三隻我覺得長玩都好玩<br />\n同唔會太chur時間刷野唔課金都一樣好玩<br />\n真心推介<br />\n其他好多手遊都幾個月內悶到棄game<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7E4wFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7E4wFU.jpg&h=b01dc9f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wG8r3wM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwG8r3wM.jpg&h=0b17d17d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fire-emblem-heroes.com/ja/sp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffire-emblem-heroes.com%2Fja%2Fsp%2F&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=30fc3051\" target=\"_blank\">https://fire-emblem-heroes.com/ja/sp/</a><br />\n呢隻火紋香港無上架<br />\n日版有得揀英文<br />\n新手都唔難上手<br />\n暫時排日本第一<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/152528_3ad58a23f6caa3757253931336408d2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F152528_3ad58a23f6caa3757253931336408d2f.jpg&h=060f78f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"864f79c01f211789ea889cf6069c5ee995f8918a","tid":113222,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"試下隻火紋先"},{"pid":"26404e2db26e688a6af407b4afdd24fe16d21a24","tid":113222,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T09:48:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下隻火紋先</blockquote><br />\n暫時零課30抽已2隻5星<br />\n<br />\n記得夠20石先抽因為可5連抽慳番5石"},{"pid":"ae0c6cd0774cfafa2eedb307e2e7ed0bba7b6095","tid":113222,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislik